window.docContents[9].resolve({"/Basic-Types/#basic-types":{"contents":"Lean 包含许多编译器特别支持的内置类型。\n有些（例如 Nat）在内核中还具有特殊支持。\n其他类型本身没有特殊的编译器支持，但出于性能原因在重要方面依赖于类型的内部表示。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考","header":"20. 基本类型","id":"/Basic-Types/#basic-types"},"/Basic-Types/Maps-and-Sets/#zh-basictypes-maps-treeset-h006":{"contents":"Returns a finite iterator over the entries of a tree set.\nThe iterator yields the elements of the set in order and then terminates.Termination properties:* Finite instance: always* Productive instance: always\n\nCheck if any element satisfies the predicate, short-circuiting if a predicate succeeds.\n\nCheck if all elements satisfy the predicate, short-circuiting if a predicate fails.\n\nFolds the given function over the elements of the tree set in ascending order.\n\nMonadically computes a value by folding the given function over the elements in the tree set in\nascending order.\n\nFolds the given function over the elements of the tree set in descending order.\n\nMonadically computes a value by folding the given function over the elements in the tree set in\ndescending order.\n\nSupport for the for loop construct in do blocks. The iteration happens in ascending\norder.\n\nCarries out a monadic action on each element in the tree set in ascending order.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009地图和套装\u0009基于树的集合","header":"20.19.10.5. 迭代","id":"/Basic-Types/Maps-and-Sets/#zh-basictypes-maps-treeset-h006"},"/Terms/Function-Application/#zh-terms-h008":{"contents":"管道语法提供了编写函数应用程序的替代方法。\n重复管道使用解析优先级而不是嵌套括号来将函数应用程序嵌套到位置参数。\n\nPipelines右管道符号将管道右侧的术语应用于其左侧的术语。左管道符号将管道左侧的术语应用于其右侧的术语。\n\n右侧管道符号背后的直觉是，左侧的值被馈送到第一个函数，其结果被馈送到第二个函数，依此类推。\n在左管道表示法中，右侧的值向左馈送。\n\nRight pipeline notation正确的管道可用于调用一个术语上的一系列函数。\n对于读者来说，他们倾向于强调正在转换的数据。#eval \"Hello!\" |> String.toList |> List.reverse |> List.head!\n'!'\n\n\nLeft pipeline notation左管道可用于调用某个术语的一系列函数。\n他们倾向于强调功能而不是数据。#eval List.head! <| List.reverse <| String.toList <| \"Hello!\"\n'!'\n\n\nPipeline Fields有一个版本的管道表示法用于 通用字段表示法。\n\ne |>.f arg 是 (e).f arg 的替代语法。Pipeline Fields有些函数不方便与管道一起使用，因为它们的参数顺序不利。\n例如，Array.push 采用数组作为其第一个参数，而不是 Nat，从而导致此错误：#eval #[1, 2, 3] |> Array.push 4\nfailed to synthesize instance of type class\n  OfNat (Array ?m.2) 4\nnumerals are polymorphic in Lean, but the numeral `4` cannot be used in a context where the expected type is\n  Array ?m.2\ndue to the absence of the instance above\n\nHint: Type class instance resolution failures can be inspected with the `set_option trace.Meta.synthInstance true` command.\n使用管道字段表示法会导致数组被插入到第一个类型正确的位置：#eval #[1, 2, 3] |>.push 4\n#[1, 2, 3, 4]\n这个过程可以迭代：#eval #[1, 2, 3] |>.push 4 |>.reverse |>.push 0 |>.reverse\n#[0, 1, 2, 3, 4]\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009条款\u0009功能应用","header":"13.4.2. 管道语法","id":"/Terms/Function-Application/#zh-terms-h008"},"/Terms/Structures-and-Constructors/#zh-terms-h014":{"contents":"匿名构造函数 和 结构实例语法 在各自的部分中进行了描述。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009条款","header":"13.6. 结构和构造函数","id":"/Terms/Structures-and-Constructors/#zh-terms-h014"},"/releases/v4.13.0/#markdown-17071411255518995340-h8":{"contents":"* #5343 允许通过注释添加 release-ci 标签 (@thorimur)* #5344 在工作流程中正确设置检查级别 (@thorimur)* #5444 Mathlib 的 lean-pr-testing-NNNN 分支应使用电池的 lean-pr-testing-NNNN 分支* #5489 更新 lean-pr-testing 分支时提交 lake-manifest.json* #5490 在 pr-release.yml 中使用单独的机密进行注释和分支\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明\u0009Lean 4.13.0 (2024-11-01)","header":"CI 的变化","id":"/releases/v4.13.0/#markdown-17071411255518995340-h8"},"/releases/v4.16.0/#markdown-17493634228065214670-h3":{"contents":"#6204 lets _ be used in numeric literals as a separator. For\nexample, 1_000_000, 0xff_ff or 0b_10_11_01_00. New lexical syntax:\n\n数字 10 : [0-9]+ (\"_\"+ [0-9]+)*\n数字2 : \"0\" [bB] (\"_\"* [0-1]+)+\n数字 8 : \"0\" [oO] (\"_\"* [0-7]+)+\n数字16：“0”[xX]（“_”* hex_char+）+\n浮点数：数字10“。”数字 10? [eE[+-]数字10]\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明\u0009Lean 4.16.0 (2025-02-03)\u0009Highlights","header":"Separators in numeric literals","id":"/releases/v4.16.0/#markdown-17493634228065214670-h3"}});